-zakat-al-fitr-sujud-sahw\/","url_meta":{"origin":31940,"position":1},"title":"Waki\u2019 on Ramadan: Zakat al-Fitr like prostration of forgetfulness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nawawi reported: Waki\u2019 ibn al-Jarrah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cZakat al-Fitr is to the month of Ramadan like the prostration of forgetfulness is to prayer. It makes up for deficiencies in fasting just as the prostration makes up for deficiencies in prayer.\u201d Source: al-Majmu\u0304\u2019 Sharh\u0323 al-Muhadhab 6\/140\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31942,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/10\/one-sa-food-zakat-al-fitr\/","url_meta":{"origin":31940,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: A portion of food due for Zakat al-Fitr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: We would bring for Zakat al-Fitr a portion of food, or a portion of barley, or a portion of dates, or a portion of cheese, or a portion of raisins. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1506, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 985 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5037,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/12\/prophet-dates-eid-al-fitr\/","url_meta":{"